      "text": "Chhattisgarh, Odisha, NE India, J&K, some parts of Himachal Pradesh, isolated places in \nUttarakhand. \n\uf0b7 Overall, rainfall is likely to be below normal over the entire country except Konkan & Goa, Madhya \n",
